OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, then brighter conditions with
OL,7,Fscattered showers gradually spread
OL,8,Feast. The showers may become heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes this afternoon. Strong winds are
OL,10,Flikely to develop along the coast for
OL,11,Fa time, then ease later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening cloud and
OL,14,Fscattered showers soon move away, then
OL,15,Fclear for a while with temperatures
OL,16,Fquickly falling. Overnight becoming
OL,17,Fcloudy again, also breezy, with
OL,18,Fperhaps isolated showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
